 =======================================
 M U L L I K E N   P O P U L A T I O N S  ***  Relaxation density (molecule minus orthogonalized fragments)  ***
 =======================================
  
 The survey below gives for each atom:
 a) the total relaxation charge (molecule minus orthogonalized fragments)
